  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">An object&rsquo;s kinetic energy, in joules, is equal to the product of one-half the object&rsquo;s mass, in kilograms, and the square of the object&rsquo;s speed, in meters per second. What is the speed, in meters per second, of an object with a mass of 4 kilograms and kinetic energy of 18 joules?</p>\n",
